# Simulator on Completion

Referenced from `AGENTS.md`. Run the simulator yourself after completing work — never ask the user to launch it.

## When to run

After completing a task that touches app code, UI, assets, or build settings:

```bash
chmod +x scripts/run-simulator.sh
./scripts/run-simulator.sh
```

## Done when

- Script exits 0
- `com.ijaejun.gumimap-v2` launches in the simulator

On failure, fix and retry before marking the task complete or updating HANDOFF.